title: 820-3115 B green light no fan spin
message: Hello I have a 820-3115-b with green light no fan spin ppbus_g3 12.55, from which I don't get PP5V_s3

title: 820-3115 B green light no fan spin
820-3115 B green light no fan spin
message: The card initially had a short on pp3v42 due to u7941, solved 3V3_S5/SUS arepresent, on q7221 ho p5vs3_en_l 3.3v

title: 820-3115 B green light no fan spin
message: Trigger SMC_ONOFF_L and check for drop pulse at PM_PWRBTN_L (at same time).

title: 820-3115 B green light no fan spin
820-3115 B green light no fan spin
message:
SMC_ONOFF_L really drops from 3V to 0V?
If yes, try reballing SMC; may need to change it.
